howItWas.description: What is drupalcamp? We took the opportunity to meet and discuss the plans for the near future of drupal. Many Chinese developers had a taste of the fun and value of this camp in Shanghai, and wanted to learn more about Drupal and its community. Therefore, we formed a team to travel to DrupalCon LA
